Database Ideas
--------------

Table : games
-------------
id : text
	id of the game of the form:
	X_AWAY_HOME_HOUR
		X : days since 3/28/2019
		AWAY : away code
		HOME : home code
		HOUR : hour the same starts

sport : text
	'MLB', 'NBA', etc.

date : datetime.date
	DDMMYYYY

game_time : datetime.time
	HH:MM


Table : mlb_538
---------------
id : text

a_starting_pitcher : text
a_team_rating : int
a_starting_pitcher_adjustment : int
a_travel_adjustment : int
a_pregame_rating : int
a_chance_winning : float
h_starting_pitcher : text
h_team_rating : int
h_starting_pitcher_adjustment :int
h_travel_adjustment : int
h_pregame_rating : int
h_chance_winning : float

Table : bets
------------
id : text

amount : int
	The amount of the bet

team : text
	'H' or 'A'

odds : int
	The odds on the team bet on


Table : outcome
---------------
id : text

outcome : int
	The amount of money gained or lost














